# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "Meer informatie"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"We werken hard aan het uitbreiden van deze gebruikershandleiding en het "
"verbeteren van OpenShot Video Editor, maar als u vastloopt en niet weet waar "
"u terecht kunt, heeft OpenShot verschillende bronnen voor aanvullende "
"informatie."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot heeft verschillende `YouTube-tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/"
"playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ beschikbaar om u te "
"helpen meer te leren."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot heeft een `Reddit-gebruikerscommunity <https://openshot.org/"
"forum>`_ die zich toelegt op gebruikers die elkaar helpen, vragen "
"beantwoorden en discussiëren over videobewerking en OpenShot-onderwerpen."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"Als u wilt helpen deze gebruikershandleiding te verbeteren, `bekijk de bron "
"op GitHub <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Als u een nieuwe bug hebt ontdekt, meld deze dan via `Rapporteer een bug "
"<https://www.openshot.org/issues/new/>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"Als u professionele ondersteuning nodig hebt, kunt u een ticket openen door "
"een bericht te sturen naar support@openshot.org of een afspraak te maken via "
"`Plan een gesprek <https://calendly.com/openshot-support/desktop>`_."
